<plot>Jan traveled trough the heavy traffic in this south Indian metropolis using the most convenient mean of transportation: The Rickshaw. Thomas was filming. But when the driver asked for the destination Jan just answered: Heaven. And surprisingly this excursion into metaphysics was not a problem for the clever drivers. The little journey takes us to different temples, to the beach (Beach is heaven? Beach is very nice!), to a big shopping mall and to a noble western Hotel.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?658914</url></doc>
